{"title":"旅泰诗草","authors":["黄天璧"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":3,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅泰诗草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄天璧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂中泰友谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸿爪雪泥忆泰京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情牵中泰倍相亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湄南扬子同携手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佛国神州日日新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咏巴提雅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景色风光世界殊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暹罗湾畔一明珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金滩碧水珊瑚岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰影婆娑入画图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠泰国诗坛泰斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王诚博士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰京聚首信前缘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倚马珠玑感赠联。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮节高风人敬仰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝翁椽笔谱新篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王诚博士为泰国著名诗人、泰国《星暹日报》诗坛主编、“国际桂冠诗人”，五分钟内为余撰一对联：“天人一体诚为贵，璧玉当前信有缘”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}